jsky.catalog.skycat
Class SkycatParamDesc

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--jsky.catalog.FieldDescAdapter
        |
        +--jsky.catalog.skycat.SkycatParamDesc
All Implemented Interfaces:
FieldDesc, java.io.Serializable
public class SkycatParamDesc
extends FieldDescAdapter

Describes a parameter to a skycat catalog query. When searching the catalog later, the parameter values (or value ranges) may be specified.

See Also:
